page.title: 08BUS SERVICES
page.content: There is a bus stop near the school.Two buses come there.Numbers 217 &number 231. The time_table for 217 is this. It starts at 5.25 & finishes at 23.40. The 217 starts its journey at Waltham Cross station & ends its journey at Turnpike Lane station. The 231 starts the journey that it has to take at Brimsdown station & ends at Turnpike Lane station. People want the buses for going to the market,shops and tube at Wood Green, and to see a relative or to see a friend. Buses are very useful for going to places like we have just said.
